WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
NYUAD provides financial support in the form of fellowships and need-based grants, 

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
to those who qualify. The support may cover up to the full 

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
cost of attendance, including tuition, foreign travel for study integral to a 

00:09.000 --> 00:13.000
student's academic program, room and board, health insurance, personal expenses, books, and 

00:13.000 --> 00:16.000
many student life activities. Financial support may also include up to two 

00:16.000 --> 00:19.000
tickets each year between Abu Dhabi and the student's country of permanent 

00:19.000 --> 00:23.000
residence. 

